Let me start by saying I have been ordering from Abide for over a year and it was always good food and good service. Today, and the last 2 times I ordered for delivery, the food was absolutely disgusting. The falafel was cold and hard, not fresh at all, the pitas were hard as a rock, the red lentil soup was watered down had no flavor or consistency, and the tahini sauce tasted old and watered down, which they make you pay extra for by the way. Extremely disappointed, and after giving them a total of 3 chances to redeem themselves, I am now over this place. They officially lost a long time customer that was ordering $25+ worth of food at least once a week.
